<p>The BedDesk attaches to your bed frame giving you a surface to use while laying in bed.</p>


<p>Perfect for Skyping friends and family, watching movies, and whatever else you want!</p>


<p>The versatility the BedDesk adds to your living environment is a welcome addition to any home.</p>


<p>This version includes a personal customization. If you select this option, please leave a note in the checkout field regarding customization and email us a 300x300 px black and white image to <strong>AskBedDesk@gmail.com</strong> with your Full Name and [Customization] in the subject heading. We'll raster your design to the wooden surface to giving your BedDesk your own personal flair.</p>
